    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sunset Arena</strong> is the ultimate casual party game, designed to bring the fun with you wherever you go. A twin or single stick top down versus shooter.  With just a Steam Deck, you can challenge a friend, or scale up for epic group battles! Inspired by the nostalgia of coffee table arcade cabinets and the excitement of arcades, <strong>Sunset Arena</strong> offers multiple control modes to suit any gathering:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Coffee Table Mode</strong>: Play up to 8 players with only 4 controllers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Couch Party Mode</strong>: Classic twin-stick battles for up to 4 players with 4 controllers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mobile Device Mode</strong>: Connect to the game via a simple web page controller and play anywhere with WiFi for up to 8 players!*</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With simple yet dynamic gameplay, anyone can jump into the action. Choose from multiple control options, including single-stick controls with auto-aim or standard twin-stick shooting, making it easy for all skill levels to join the fun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Plenty of Game Modes</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Derezz Match (Death Match)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capture the Flag</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >King of the Hill</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arena Ball</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss Battle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survival Waves</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Energy Collection<br><br><br>*Web controller performance depends on network connection stability, the responsiveness may vary.  </p></li></ul>",
